$ $ORACLE_HOME/apex/apex_rest_config.sql

`apex_rest_config.sql` configures *RESTful services* and creates the `APEX_LISTENER` and `APEX_REST_PUBLIC_USER` database users. 

This script is expected to be run under `sys as sysdba`.

code {
sys@ORA19> @apex_rest_config.sql
Enter a password for the APEX_LISTENER user              []
Enter a password for the APEX_REST_PUBLIC_USER user              []
...set_appun.sql
...create APEX_LISTENER and APEX_REST_PUBLIC_USER users
code }
